name: "You disappear" by Cinthia Ponce
description:
I've been calling your name in this universe
You appear in my imagination
As if you were really there
But when I want to embrace you
Suddenly, you disappear
From all the memories stored in my heart
I feel you with every burst of pain.

Image source: pexels
Intervention, customization and collage of images. Conceptual art.
